  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/c954e7a04f85b8d4ce64e37822b2254e.poster.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/c954e7a04f85b8d4ce64e37822b2254e.webm?t=1730111123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/b0335362d0f13eecc4a22fe0b4d17768.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leshy Prelude is a <strong>20-30 minute action-adventure experience</strong>. It contains graphics inspired by the rendering limitations of PSX along with gun-play mechanics that encourage puzzle-solving/timing with a mix of movement, reaction times, and aiming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy boomer shooters with a mix of story elements, you'll more than likely enjoy this for the challenge and intrigue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/ee8907c8dc903d3b783026784058d254.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A mysterious and gripping story as you uncover the horrors of the forest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > FPS Action with (relatively) fast-paced gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mechanics that work in-tandem to encourage quick-thinking, precise timing, and satisfying execution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Controller Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Classic PSX-inspired graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A State-of-the-art investigative licking experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/82ba29bdd4f4cb706f0f32811bc9882b.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Profiles and some background about the characters within Leshy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/85b888619193b4f8b3e79def241cbe61.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/27ddacf4233baf973c0ff43e9c620f39.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/dc69255049a80040e834cfde7824ae3c.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/a29f0418d55813dbe8ea76d7d44946fd.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/f63bb1b002930ee9173427bdc3b0934c.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/c954e7a04f85b8d4ce64e37822b2254e.poster.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/c954e7a04f85b8d4ce64e37822b2254e.webm?t=1730111123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/b0335362d0f13eecc4a22fe0b4d17768.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leshy Prelude is a <strong>20-30 minute action-adventure experience</strong>. It contains graphics inspired by the rendering limitations of PSX along with gun-play mechanics that encourage puzzle-solving/timing with a mix of movement, reaction times, and aiming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy boomer shooters with a mix of story elements, you'll more than likely enjoy this for the challenge and intrigue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/ee8907c8dc903d3b783026784058d254.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A mysterious and gripping story as you uncover the horrors of the forest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > FPS Action with (relatively) fast-paced gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mechanics that work in-tandem to encourage quick-thinking, precise timing, and satisfying execution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Controller Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Classic PSX-inspired graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A State-of-the-art investigative licking experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam Achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/82ba29bdd4f4cb706f0f32811bc9882b.avif?t=1730111123\" width=616 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Profiles and some background about the characters within Leshy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/85b888619193b4f8b3e79def241cbe61.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/27ddacf4233baf973c0ff43e9c620f39.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/dc69255049a80040e834cfde7824ae3c.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/a29f0418d55813dbe8ea76d7d44946fd.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182020/extras/f63bb1b002930ee9173427bdc3b0934c.avif?t=1730111123\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
